ClusteringSettings pl.mg6.android.maps.extensions.ClusteringSettings.clusterSize ( double  clusterSize  ) 

Consider using value of 180, 160, 144, 120 or 96 for 8x8, 9x9, 10x10, 12x12 and 15x15 grids respectively on zoom level 2.

Parameters:
clusterSize cluster size in degrees of longitude on zoom level 0.
